    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2008 Porsche Cayman S featuring the 3.4L M97.21 flat-six powerplant paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. This mid-engine platform excels in rotational inertia balance, providing exceptional turn-in and corner-exit stability. The VarioCam Plus system delivers a broad torque curve, while the hydraulic steering rack offers the unfiltered feedback modern EPAS systems lack. This example features a recently refreshed cooling system and a clean borescope report, ensuring the integrity of the Nikasil-coated cylinder walls. While the aesthetics reflect honest road use, the chassis remains taut and the factory PASM dampers are fully functional, making this a turn-key option for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
